title: Velo Bed and Breakfast
description: Organic B&B located just outside Eugene on lovely wooded acreage in the heart of wine country. Vegan breakfast and dessert served by the founder of Eugene's Morning Glory Cafe. USA-made products throughout, cork flooring, modern decor. One rescued happy cow named Peanut invites you to come and meet him. Mention HappyCow and receive a 10% discount.
